step: Set viewport size to width 1080 and height 1440
Visit URL assigned to variable "app.url"
Enter "Admin" in the "Username" text field
Click on the "Password" text field
Enter a password in the "Password" text field
Click on the "Login" button
Assert "innerText" of the <h6> element with text "Dashboard" equals "Dashboard"
Click on the <span> element with text "Admin"
Click on the "Add" button
Assert "innerText" of the <h6> element with text "Add User" equals "Add User"
Click on the <i> element with class name "oxd-icon bi-caret-up-fill oxd-select-text--arrow"
Click on the <div> element with text "Admin"
Click on the <i> element with class name "oxd-icon bi-caret-up-fill oxd-select-text--arrow"
Click on the <div> element with text "Enabled"
Click on the "Type for hints..." text field
Enter "john" in the "Type for hints..." text field
Send "[ENTER]" keypress to the "Type for hints..." text field
Click on the <div> element with text "joker john selvam"
Click on the "Username" text field
Enter {{userName}} in the "Username" text field
Click on the "Password" text field
Insert value of variable "password" into the "Password" text field
Click on the "Confirm Password" text field
Enter a password in the "Confirm Password" text field
Assert "value" of the "Username" text field equals the value of the variable "userName"
Click on the "Save" button
Click on the <i> element with class name "oxd-icon bi-caret-down-fill oxd-userdropdown-icon"
Click on the link "Logout" to https://opensource-demo...eb/index.php/auth/logout
Assert "innerText" of the <div> element with text "Username : Admin Password : admin123" equals "Username : Admin Password : admin123"
